{"tid":1056912,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"住緊英國/想移居英國同我入一入黎玩遊戲！","createTime":"2019-03-11T13:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T03:20:49.000Z","uid":208927,"like":11,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"84df03184ad9fa3e96e94637923b19dfa823edb2","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"純粹意見調查<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGhtwNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGhtwNc.png&h=173c455a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞：「距離2047年正式回歸不足十年，唔少市民......」<br />\n<br />\n你係一家之主，聽到呢則新聞你知道係時候準備帶家人去英國定居。你為今日等待左二十年，但宜家心情十分複雜：<br />\n<br />\n1. 怕就讀小學嘅仔唔習慣英國新生活<br />\n2. 怕小朋友入讀本地學校俾人欺負<br />\n3. 活左係香港幾十年去到要花一段時間適應<br />\n4. 去到英國冇乜朋友冇乜照應<br />\n5. 再過一代怕個孫唔識講廣東話<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n你開左一罐啤酒，講左句：<br />\n唉好燃煩，諗住邊再算！<br />\n<br />\n你會選擇：<br />\n<br />\nA. 大城市 （ London, Birmingham, Manchester )<br />\n-交通方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-購物方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-龍蛇混雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB. 城市 （ Worcester, Lancaster, Oxford... )<br />\n-交通相對方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-生活購物都方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-冇噤雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC. 內陸小城鎮 （ 有火車站個啲, 冇火車站唔考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n-有火車出城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-環境清幽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-冇乜野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD. 南部沿海城市 （ Eastbound, Brighton... )<br />\n-習慣香港有海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有海睇身心舒暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-生活冇大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房屋種類：<br />\n1. Detached house <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yVbuJP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yVbuJP.png&h=0e5dc048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. Terraced house<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymjjDCa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymjjDCa.png&h=39d4380b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. Bungalow<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgHtwXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgHtwXb.png&h=2e203bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. Flat<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSp35hb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSp35hb.png&h=01cdbac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你係到考慮之際<br />\n你父母send 左個訊息畀你<br />\n你打開一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來英國有一個地方起左一個大屋苑<br />\n單位都係兩層獨立屋<br />\n有花園仔同天台<br />\n望落有啲九龍塘嘅影子<br />\n查一查發現裏面住都係同你差不多背景嘅香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ4C9Tz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ4C9Tz.png&h=53b53d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-全部新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-有同鄉互相照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-環境相對熟悉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />退休一流<br />\n-過時過節熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />互相拜年<br />\n-有人會明白你思鄉情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-位於一個你未聽過嘅鎮/城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-交通還可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（出大城市/機場）<br />\n-仔女就讀最近中小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知道大家會點選擇<br />\n<br />\n正皮：同埋其他香港人一齊住，將香港家帶過去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮：入鄉隨俗，融入下英國生活幾好！寫低你選擇同點解 （ e.g B3 唔想噤偏僻，人老唔行噤多樓梯，唔大唔細好打掃 ）"},{"pid":"0874618818e3a83f206d866cf33509c7e84e6bb5","tid":1056912,"uid":237240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd1aa092cdf9cd7b8dbad873d01b111307482bee","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0874618818e3a83f206d866cf33509c7e84e6bb5","tid":1056912,"uid":237240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf269475a544d297b956375be5e7eab6b7b3d74","tid":1056912,"uid":202412,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"沿岸for sure 去過返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff92b91e55f96599d8a3a4b6fd599caeef517b77","tid":1056912,"uid":35846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:58:09.000Z","msg":"大環區for sure"},{"pid":"c6def706dc0254eba3779367e458dac304783514","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf269475a544d297b956375be5e7eab6b7b3d74","tid":1056912,"uid":202412,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"沿岸for sure 去過返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"岩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起身上balcony 飲杯咖啡望下海<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇海就要有山，之前stay過一個town得平地唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69863090b85d5df0f05dce01cc860ea29dfc3d4d","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"cornwall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊要有架車，得閒揸吓啲british b roads，揸完返屋企就去沙灘行下，先係最撚正。"},{"pid":"35ef98708bfde3f8a4cf2b9f49dc58c2325b2767","tid":1056912,"uid":129992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"E. 太怕老豆長腳，未儲夠錢開中國外賣餐館昆鬼佬，選擇留係香港踎住先再申請綠卡去美國"},{"pid":"c6e684fbee1d4a5518daa1e41e8a34b118cecc58","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69863090b85d5df0f05dce01cc860ea29dfc3d4d","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"cornwall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊要有架車，得閒揸吓啲british b roads，揸完返屋企就去沙灘行下，先係最撚正。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fb93e5438ad1d39b233e48694af20b94561d59","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ef98708bfde3f8a4cf2b9f49dc58c2325b2767","tid":1056912,"uid":129992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"E. 太怕老豆長腳，未儲夠錢開中國外賣餐館昆鬼佬，選擇留係香港踎住先再申請綠卡去美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實開餐館應該唔難，租唔係特別貴，經just eat/deliveroo應該都有得做"},{"pid":"807e3149e1eb9d2d7e858399d16e7493366d2262","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1fb93e5438ad1d39b233e48694af20b94561d59","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ef98708bfde3f8a4cf2b9f49dc58c2325b2767","tid":1056912,"uid":129992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"E. 太怕老豆長腳，未儲夠錢開中國外賣餐館昆鬼佬，選擇留係香港踎住先再申請綠卡去美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實開餐館應該唔難，租唔係特別貴，經just eat/deliveroo應該都有得做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"英國係稅重，租還可以<br />\n雖然話460,000一年樓下都係20%<br />\n但香港扣稅+免稅額可以差好遠<br />\n仲要畀national insurance"},{"pid":"e5465589ca4edd2b7e5847c03379dfffcd8b847f","tid":1056912,"uid":222834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"B4<br />\n鍾意唔太大嘅大城市，多啲英國本土人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該會揀Oxford/Bath (有文化+歷史氣息，普遍有教養，有河，南部英文好聽啲）<br />\n不過應該會好掛住個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住就唔駛太大，反正flat 都普遍大過香港，清潔方便啲又有安全感啲視野又好啲，仲要有lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好嘅係唔知點解佢哋啲flat 好興一入門口，最近就係睡房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：住過吓爛鬼小城市"},{"pid":"34fc053b02a2287759824b3c6fe8dff067e2531a","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"807e3149e1eb9d2d7e858399d16e7493366d2262","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a1fb93e5438ad1d39b233e48694af20b94561d59","tid":1056912,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35ef98708bfde3f8a4cf2b9f49dc58c2325b2767","tid":1056912,"uid":129992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"E. 太怕老豆長腳，未儲夠錢開中國外賣餐館昆鬼佬，選擇留係香港踎住先再申請綠卡去美國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:29:30.000Z","msg":"其實開餐館應該唔難，租唔係特別貴，經just eat/deliveroo應該都有得做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"英國係稅重，租還可以<br />\n雖然話460,000一年樓下都係20%<br />\n但香港扣稅+免稅額可以差好遠<br />\n仲要畀national insurance"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"師兄好似有啲心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 2012過嚟嘅留學生"},{"pid":"2950ef4d133becf63303fe5399b071ab003916cb","tid":1056912,"uid":32661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"我會想住大城市邊緣但又近火車站交通方便既地方<br />\n好似reading 咁<br />\n40分鐘落到zone 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2785436f8b1204bda15ce68581b71e018d89580","tid":1056912,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:54:27.000Z","msg":"大城市suburb<br />\n我去london 通常住ealing<br />\n細得黎咩都有，好方便"},{"pid":"19a80870466dad7cfd6134b58e27a732bedba894","tid":1056912,"uid":226199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84df03184ad9fa3e96e94637923b19dfa823edb2","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T13:51:00.000Z","msg":"純粹意見調查<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGhtwNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGhtwNc.png&h=173c455a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新聞：「距離2047年正式回歸不足十年，唔少市民......」<br />\n<br />\n你係一家之主，聽到呢則新聞你知道係時候準備帶家人去英國定居。你為今日等待左二十年，但宜家心情十分複雜：<br />\n<br />\n1. 怕就讀小學嘅仔唔習慣英國新生活<br />\n2. 怕小朋友入讀本地學校俾人欺負<br />\n3. 活左係香港幾十年去到要花一段時間適應<br />\n4. 去到英國冇乜朋友冇乜照應<br />\n5. 再過一代怕個孫唔識講廣東話<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n你開左一罐啤酒，講左句：<br />\n唉好燃煩，諗住邊再算！<br />\n<br />\n你會選擇：<br />\n<br />\nA. 大城市 （ London, Birmingham, Manchester )<br />\n-交通方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-購物方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-龍蛇混雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB. 城市 （ Worcester, Lancaster, Oxford... )<br />\n-交通相對方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-生活購物都方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-冇噤雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nC. 內陸小城鎮 （ 有火車站個啲, 冇火車站唔考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n-有火車出城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-環境清幽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-冇乜野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD. 南部沿海城市 （ Eastbound, Brighton... )<br />\n-習慣香港有海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有海睇身心舒暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-生活冇大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n房屋種類：<br />\n1. Detached house <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yVbuJP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yVbuJP.png&h=0e5dc048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. Terraced house<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ymjjDCa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FymjjDCa.png&h=39d4380b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. Bungalow<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgHtwXb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgHtwXb.png&h=2e203bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. Flat<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSp35hb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSp35hb.png&h=01cdbac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當你係到考慮之際<br />\n你父母send 左個訊息畀你<br />\n你打開一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來英國有一個地方起左一個大屋苑<br />\n單位都係兩層獨立屋<br />\n有花園仔同天台<br />\n望落有啲九龍塘嘅影子<br />\n查一查發現裏面住都係同你差不多背景嘅香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ4C9Tz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ4C9Tz.png&h=53b53d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-樓價可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-全部新樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-有同鄉互相照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-環境相對熟悉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />退休一流<br />\n-過時過節熱鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />互相拜年<br />\n-有人會明白你思鄉情懷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-位於一個你未聽過嘅鎮/城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-交通還可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（出大城市/機場）<br />\n-仔女就讀最近中小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想知道大家會點選擇<br />\n<br />\n正皮：同埋其他香港人一齊住，將香港家帶過去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮：入鄉隨俗，融入下英國生活幾好！寫低你選擇同點解 （ e.g B3 唔想噤偏僻，人老唔行噤多樓梯，唔大唔細好打掃 ）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:57:48.000Z","msg":"點解唔揾下倫敦南外圍既county? Surrey 學校網全英最好， 近倫敦比較 multi-cultural。 <br />\n<br />\n香港人比較鐘意apartment， 有management唔洗自己整屋， 唔好處係多數係leasehold， 幾十年就要保地價一次。 <br />\n<br />\n生活同香港無得比較， 基本上係apple同orange， 不過只要有架車就方便好多。"},{"pid":"c1eb334247d5eac2440619b244e3daa23baf987c","tid":1056912,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"讀書都仲可以 做嘢退休不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5dc1e5554a8f8e7ad41563a2772f666c2c4238","tid":1056912,"uid":2603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"小朋友方面驚你個仔俾人bully 不如驚佢bully返人好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬼仔year11 six form 先開始發育 <br />\n<br />\n由細一齊讀書 基本上 去到中學frd過打band <br />\n佢地普遍係 幼稚園就已經係果班人 去到alevel 所以小學過去都唔洗點擔心 可以話係上一輩都係咁"},{"pid":"1e2085906cda27d0f3b6a879ee2e7d880e81b3b5","tid":1056912,"uid":241356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:08:01.000Z","msg":"之前去左york幾鐘意佢嗰邊嘅氣氛 有錢想係嗰邊退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有間意大利手工雪糕超好食<br />\n<br />\nBrighton都幾好 但個Brighton pier冇乜好玩 有個博物館好多以前清朝啲野(好似係?)個度個下午茶幾正 仲有好多同性戀酒吧<br />\n<br />\nLake District 有山有湖有海 但可惜冬天就唔住得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bfda1e87a1751c5210d83271b0d4be0c25a4af","tid":1056912,"uid":203833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:28:56.000Z","msg":"Sheffield, detached house.<br />\nor<br />\nBirmingham, flat.<br />\n同前女友都好鐘意Sheffield，我地都住過Birmingham市中心（B1）既Flat，懷念下感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8590548a3b8f9bd2cf83917a67d0b77be835262f","tid":1056912,"uid":34206,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"作為一隻獌狗, 有得揀既話想去Manchester, 求其住apartment都可以, 但驚過去搵唔到野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: BC但未去過英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f8951227c424261e4ecfb612d55fc6cf1aa602","tid":1056912,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5465589ca4edd2b7e5847c03379dfffcd8b847f","tid":1056912,"uid":222834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T14:35:50.000Z","msg":"B4<br />\n鍾意唔太大嘅大城市，多啲英國本土人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該會揀Oxford/Bath (有文化+歷史氣息，普遍有教養，有河，南部英文好聽啲）<br />\n不過應該會好掛住個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住就唔駛太大，反正flat 都普遍大過香港，清潔方便啲又有安全感啲視野又好啲，仲要有lift<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好嘅係唔知點解佢哋啲flat 好興一入門口，最近就係睡房<img 